ast lake in the center, keeping an eye out for exciting wildlife and unique plants. Plus, the buzzing streets filled with coconut sellers and stalls are just a stone&#x2019;s throw away from this fantastic nature.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-590x810.jpg\" alt=\"kandy market\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"kandy market\" class=\"wp-image-75359 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-590x810.jpg 590w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-437x600.jpg 437w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-246x338.jpg 246w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-131x180.jpg 131w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-560x768.jpg 560w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-746x1024.jpg 746w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-787x1080.jpg 787w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-1049x1440.jpg 1049w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05210400\/sri-lanka-route-1-300x412.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.sa