roup\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Don&#x2019;t forget to pay a visit to the Royal Botanical Gardens, a fantastic tranquil wilderness in the city, full of a diverse range of plants, trees, and flowers. As you look around, you&#x2019;ll notice that the mountains and tropical rainforests are never far away! It&#x2019;s this proximity that makes Kandy a great jumping-off point for day trips.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">9 Things to do in Kandy<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__wrapper video-block__wrapper--breakout\" itemscope itemtype=\"https:\/\/schema.org\/VideoObject\">\n                <h3 class=\"video-block__wrapper-title\" itemprop=\"name\">Sri Lanka<\/h3>\n\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnail\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152400\/Thumb-Thebeautyof-SriLanka-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Sri Lanka\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\" content=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152400\/Thumb-Thebeautyof-SriLanka-800x450.jpg\">\n                <meta itemprop=\"uploadDate\" content=\"2018-07-02 16:06:57\">\n\n\n                <div class=\"video-block video-block--mediavine\">\n                    <div class=\"video-block__embed\">\n                        <div class=\"mv-video-target mv-video-id-d9dlr5yjewfgvdxeqruh\" data-video-id=\"d9dlr5yjewfgvdxeqruh\" data-volume=\"70\" data-ratio=\"16:9\" data-autoinsert=\"true\" data-disable-jsonld=\"true\"><\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n                <a class=\"video-block__credit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/c\/saltinourhair?sub_confirmation=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"YouTube Salt in our Hair\">\n                    <div class=\"socials__item\">\n                        <span class=\"socials__link\">\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-youtube\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-youtube\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <span>Subscribe to our <b>YouTube channel<\/b> and never miss a video!<\/span>\n                <\/a>\n\n                <div class=\"video-block__bg\">\n                    <img class=\"video-block__bg-image lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/23152400\/Thumb-Thebeautyof-SriLanka-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"Sri Lanka\" height=\"450\" width=\"800\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"day-4-sigiriya\">Day 4: Sigiriya<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Lion Rock in Sigiriya is one of the country&#x2019;s most famous landmarks. The enormous natural formation sticks out of the flat landscape, towering above forests and grasslands filled with elephants. On top of the 200-meter square-shaped rock, you&#x2019;ll find the remains of an ancient palace and gardens and many rock drawings along the way. Additionally, Lion Rock is one of the eight <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/destinations\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO World Heritage sites<\/a> in Sri Lanka, which is another reason to add it to your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a> route!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-3 is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-7231 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/23154642\/sigiriya-lion-rock-sri-lanka-archeology-614x