te, taking you through stunning rolling hilltops, rainforest, and luscious green tea plantations. Hang out the door with the wind in your hair and feel the weather get cooler as you move higher up into the mist and the clouds of the Sri Lanka highlands. Get <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/kandy\/ella\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy Train Tickets here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/sri-lanka-train-kandy-ella\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kandy to Ella Train<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05211835\/sri-lanka-route-8.jpg\" alt=\"train travel kandy ella\"><\/noscript><img width=\"236\" height=\"338\" alt=\"train travel kandy ella\" class=\"wp-image-75371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1343px) 100vw, 1343px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05211835\/sri-lanka-route-8.jpg 1343w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05211835\/sri-lanka-route-8-420x600.jpg 420w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05211835\/sri-lanka-route-8-567x810.jpg 567w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05211835\/sri-lanka-ro