est.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2619&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05235222\/sri-lanka-travel-route-5.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05235222\/sri-lanka-travel-route-5-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/05235222\/sri-lanka-travel-route-5-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Sri Lanka Travel Guide: a 3-week travel itinerary\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"day-8-10-ella\">Day 8 &#x2013; 10: Ella<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit one of the most blissful and natural places in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>: Ella. The small town has a laid-back hippy vibe, complemented by the great mountains and hills that tower over the town. Stay in a hilltop guesthouse with incredible views, and use it as a base to climb to Adams Peak, Ella Rock, or the mesmerizing <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/nine-arch-bridge-ella\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nine Arch Bridge<\/a>. When you&#x2019;re done hiking, head for one of the many picturesque waterfall pools for a refreshing dip.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ella is one of the most beautiful places in the country and an absolute <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/must-do-sri-lanka\/\">must-do in Sri Lanka<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Things To Do in Ella, Sri Lanka<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-648x810.jpg\" alt=\"Things to do Ella Sri Lanka little adams peak\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Things to do Ella Sri Lanka little adams peak\" class=\"wp-image-6587 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-Sri-Lanka-little-adams-peak-2-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/11\/23155646\/Things-to-do-Ella-S