nka\/arugam-bay-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Things To Do in Arugam Bay<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-2 is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-798x810.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches arugam bay\"><\/noscript><img width=\"333\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka beaches arugam bay\" class=\"wp-image-6805 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 798px) 100vw, 798px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-798x810.jpg 798w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-300x304.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-600x609.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-333x338.jpg 333w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-591x600.jpg 591w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-30x30.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-161x163.jpg 161w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-177x180.jpg 177w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-757x768.jpg 757w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155235\/arugam-bay-guide-things-to-do-art-1009x1024.jpg 1009w, https:\/\/st